1. Suggestions now bypass translation (skipTranslation flag)
   - Picking a suggestion no longer re-translates the already-correct word
   - Translation buffer cleared on suggestion pick

2. Clipboard paste bypasses translation
   - Pasting 'hello' no longer gets transliterated

3. Voice input bypasses translation
   - Speech-to-text output committed as-is

4. KeyView.performLongClick() now calls super
   - Required for proper Android accessibility chain
   - Was missing super call which breaks a11y event propagation
